00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:36,140
No one else.

146
00:08:37,900 --> 00:08:39,220
I came to you straight away.

147
00:08:41,060 --> 00:08:41,780
I don't know

148
00:08:43,060 --> 00:08:44,060
