168
00:09:53,420 --> 00:09:54,980
Do you want to apply to a police academy?

169
00:09:56,900 --> 00:09:57,820
Anti-narcotics?

170
00:10:12,460 --> 00:10:13,340
I have faith in you.

171
00:10:14,820 --> 00:10:17,020
You can separate emotions from your duty.

172
00:10:22,300 --> 00:10:22,820
Of course.

173
00:10:24,660 --> 00:10:25,300
I understand.

174
00:10:26,740 --> 00:10:27,780
I am a policewoman.

175
00:10:30,380 --> 00:10:31,140
Vice Captain Chen.

176
00:10:32,220 --> 00:10:32,900
I should be going now.

177
