192
00:12:10,740 --> 00:12:11,540
from your piece.

193
00:12:29,860 --> 00:12:31,420
Dusan is my buddy

194
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:32,900
but the death of your father

195
00:12:33,020 --> 00:12:35,460
has nothing to do with me.

196
00:12:37,380 --> 00:12:38,420
You...

197
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:39,860
Don't tell Dong

198
00:12:40,020 --> 00:12:41,420
that I produced drugs behind his back.

199
00:12:42,460 --> 00:12:44,100
If he knows about it,

200
00:12:44,460 --> 00:12:45,940
I'll die.

201
00:12:46,700 --> 00:12:47,540
I want to see Dong.

202
00:12:47,540 --> 00:12:51,620
[Hu Qingshan, Drug Dealer]

203
00:13:00,860 --> 00:13:02,060
If you tell Dong

204
00:13:02,060 --> 00:13:02,940
what I'm doing,

205
00:13:03,140 --> 00:13:04,420
