how did he meet Hu Qingshan?

296
00:16:34,820 --> 00:16:35,700
He didn't tell us about it.

297
00:16:36,780 --> 00:16:38,100
After I interrogated him,

298
00:16:38,380 --> 00:16:39,460
I believe the reason he came back

299
00:16:39,460 --> 00:16:40,140
and did all these

300
00:16:40,420 --> 00:16:41,620
was related to the death of his father

301
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:42,740
three years ago.

302
00:16:43,060 --> 00:16:44,100
I once suggested combining both cases...

303
00:16:44,380 --> 00:16:45,260
Of course, he wouldn't

304
00:16:45,260 --> 00:16:45,980
tell you everything.

305
00:16:48,700 --> 00:16:50,140
We have arrested drug addicts before.

306
00:16:50,780 --> 00:16:51,980
As long as we can't locate their drugs,

307
00:16:52,380 --> 00:16:53,180
they will deny everything.

308
00:16:54,380 --> 00:16:55,460
They will make themselves

309
00:16:55,940 --> 00:16:56,940
look as favorable

310
00:16:56,940 --> 00:16:57,780
as possible.

311
00:16:59,540 --> 00:17:00,580
So, continue investigating.

312
00:17:03,740 --> 00:17:04,660
Two pointers.

313
00:17:06,060 --> 00:17:06,580
First,

314
00:17:07,380 --> 00:17:09,380
find out what Wu Zhenfeng did

315
00:17:10,060 --> 00:17:11,980
the night Hu Qingshan died.

316
00:17:12,580 --> 00:17:14,420
Second, find this Huang Daxian

317
00:17:14,420 --> 00:17:15,380
as soon as possible.

318
00:17:16,700 --> 00:17:17,260
It's getting late.

319
00:17:17,900 --> 00:17:18,420
Let's end the meeting.

320
00:17:46,140 --> 00:17:46,620
Something to report!

321
00:17:47,340 --> 00:17:47,820
Come in.

322
00:17:55,940 --> 00:17:56,780
Captain Liu.

323
00:17:58,980 --> 00:17:59,780
I want to know

324
00:18:00,900 --> 00:18:01,700
why you asked me to leave

325
00:18:01,700 --> 00:18:02,700
during the interrogation.

326
00:18:03,740 --> 00:18:04,660
Is it because you don't trust me?

327
00:18:08,220 --> 00:18:08,820
If I don't trust you,

328
00:18:08,820 --> 00:18:09,980
why would I bring you in here?

329
00:18:09,980 --> 00:18:10,860
Where is your logic?

330
00:18:15,100 --> 00:18:15,980
Go back and rest up.

331
00:18:16,060 --> 00:18:17,020
Tomorrow morning, Yang Yi and you

332
00:18:17,020 --> 00:18:18,780
will look for that skewers restaurant.

333
00:18:19,940 --> 00:18:20,460
Captain Liu.

334
00:18:21,340 --> 00:18:22,340
We have Wu Zhenfeng now.

335
00:18:22,820 --> 00:18:23,900
I want to solve that case

336
00:18:23,900 --> 00:18:24,740
from three years ago.

337
00:18:25,380 --> 00:18:26,820
I don't want any mystery.

338
00:18:30,700 --> 00:18:31,420
There is no mystery.

339
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:35,580
The suspect was killed on the spot

340
00:18:36,340 --> 00:18:37,460
and Wu Zhenfeng fled.

341
00:18:38,500 --> 00:18:39,900
To arrest him,

342
00:18:40,020 --> 00:18:41,100
you left the jurisdiction on your own

343
00:18:41,260 --> 00:18:42,900
and committed a grave mistake.

344
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:44,420
But since you're still young,

345
00:18:44,420 --> 00:18:46,140
you are not expelled.

346
00:19:00,140 --> 00:19:01,740
The moment you brought him
into the interrogation room,

347
00:19:01,980 --> 00:19:03,340
I could tell from your eyes

348
00:19:03,340 --> 00:19:05,060
that you were on the verge of losing control.

349
00:19:05,980 --> 00:19:07,660
He noticed that too

350
00:19:07,860 --> 00:19:08,780
so he kept provoking you.

351
00:19:09,420 --> 00:19:10,420
I did not lose control.

352
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:11,700
But you could have.

353
00:19:12,900 --> 00:19:14,260
It was a possibility

354
00:19:14,740 --> 00:19:15,940
and it shouldn't be there in the first place.

355
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:16,460
Am I right?

356
00:19:20,460 --> 00:19:21,220
I asked him

357
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:22,580
about how you arrested him

358
00:19:22,580 --> 00:19:24,020
to protect you.

359
00:19:25,380 --> 00:19:27,380
After all, you fired twice, didn't you?

360
00:19:27,900 --> 00:19:28,780
Twice.

361
00:19:30,020 --> 00:19:30,500
Captain Liu.

362
00:19:31,180 --> 00:19:33,060
I have given my justification.

363
00:19:33,980 --> 00:19:35,420
I believe in your justification.

364
00:19:36,180 --> 00:19:37,780
He is the only lead we have regarding

365
00:19:37,780 --> 00:19:38,540
the rhubarb capsule case.

366
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:40,940
But since you once leaked our operation

367
00:19:40,940 --> 00:19:41,940
to him,

368
00:19:41,940 --> 00:19:43,300
you should keep a low profile.

369
00:19:43,860 --> 00:19:44,500
Don't you agree?

370
00:19:51,980 --> 00:19:52,820
Ask yourself.

371
00:19:53,260 --> 00:19:53,860
What is more important?

372
00:19:53,860 --> 00:19:54,820
The case

373
00:19:54,860 --> 00:19:55,540
from three years ago

374
00:19:55,580 --> 00:19:56,260
or the rhubarb capsule case

375
00:19:56,260 --> 00:19:57,500
at the moment?

376
00:20:00,180 --> 00:20:01,340
Don't give me the answer now.

377
00:20:03,020 --> 00:20:03,980
Think it through.

378
00:20:10,020 --> 00:20:14,540
[Mixiang]

379
00:20:29,820 --> 00:20:31,540
Officer Chen from the Counter Narcotics Unit.

380
00:20:36,620 --> 00:20:38,020
I bought your favorite supper.

381
00:20:38,180 --> 00:20:38,860
Should we cook it?

382
00:20:42,620 --> 00:20:43,540
Didn't I say no need

383
00:20:44,020 --> 00:20:45,460
to wait for me after 10PM?

384
00:20:45,740 --> 00:20:46,900
I'm tired. I won't eat.

385
00:20:47,740 --> 00:20:48,380
Stop right there.

386
00:21:08,340 --> 00:21:09,100
What?

387
00:21:09,580 --> 00:21:10,460
You even opened a wine bottle.

388
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:15,740
What's the matter?

389
00:21:16,620 --> 00:21:17,820
I wanted to celebrate with you because

390
00:21:17,820 --> 00:21:19,060
you caught a drug addict this time.

391
00:21:21,260 --> 00:21:21,820
Yang Yi told you?

392
00:21:22,900 --> 00:21:23,540
Him?

393
00:21:25,340 --> 00:21:26,700
You know he's a stickler for rules.

394
00:21:26,900 --> 00:21:27,260
You

395
00:21:27,260 --> 00:21:28,580
shouldn't hide secrets from me.

396
00:21:28,780 --> 00:21:29,980
This province is not huge per se.

397
00:21:30,420 --> 00:21:31,060
Didn't you issue a call

398
00:21:31,060 --> 00:21:32,580
for assistance this afternoon?

399
00:21:33,420 --> 00:21:34,300
The news is all over

400
00:21:34,340 --> 00:21:35,340
the place these few days.

401
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:47,020
The one I arrested today

402
00:21:49,620 --> 00:21:50,820
is the neighbor I had

403
00:21:52,740 --> 00:21:53,780
I told you last night.

404
00:22:01,060 --> 00:22:01,900
Isn't it great?

405
00:22:02,260 --> 00:22:03,060
At least

406
00:22:04,020 --> 00:22:05,620
you can sort out everything from three years ago

407
00:22:06,380 --> 00:22:07,620
with your colleagues.

408
00:22:10,620 --> 00:22:11,620
We interrogated him for a night.

409
00:22:12,580 --> 00:22:13,340
It only brings more questions.

410
00:22:17,740 --> 00:22:18,540
You're a spoilsport.

411
00:22:19,140 --> 00:22:20,260
I don't think you want to drink with me

412
00:22:20,260 --> 00:22:21,060
at all.

413
00:22:23,060 --> 00:22:23,500
Forget it.

414
00:22:24,420 --> 00:22:25,900
Go to bed.

415
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:27,060
Just so you know,

416
00:22:27,420 --> 00:22:28,500
you're in the Counter Narcotics Unit now.

417
00:22:28,500 --> 00:22:29,540
It's not a normal police station.

418
00:22:29,980 --> 00:22:30,980
Rinse yourself and sleep.

419
00:22:31,340 --> 00:22:32,500
I'll lock everything else.

420
00:22:33,340 --> 00:22:33,900
Also,

421
00:22:34,060 --> 00:22:35,260
don't you ever come here again

422
00:22:35,260 --> 00:22:36,340
bearing negative feelings
you've had in the police force.

423
00:22:36,500 --> 00:22:37,260
Do you hear me?

424
00:22:37,700 --> 00:22:38,540
I do.

425
00:22:42,580 --> 00:22:43,180
Careful!

426
00:22:43,300 --> 00:22:43,780
The flowers.

427
00:22:44,380 --> 00:22:45,260
I did notice them.

428
00:22:51,820 --> 00:22:53,900
This door seems to be getting a bit jammed.

429
00:22:55,100 --> 00:22:56,340
If so, you should have someone fix it.

430
00:22:56,860 --> 00:22:57,660
Someone?

431
00:22:57,980 --> 00:22:59,060
Who don't you fix it for me?

432
00:23:00,020 --> 00:23:01,140
I don't have time for it.

433
00:23:03,700 --> 00:23:04,180
How about this?

434
00:23:04,460 --> 00:23:05,220
Ask Zhang

435
00:23:05,660 --> 00:23:06,420
to get someone fix it.

436
00:23:07,060 --> 00:23:07,420
Fine.

437
00:23:08,540 --> 00:23:09,580
Mind your hands.

438
00:23:10,700 --> 00:23:18,700
[Detainment Cell]

439
00:23:38,980 --> 00:23:39,740
(Erliang.)

440
00:23:40,380 --> 00:23:41,540
(I've been found out by)

441
00:23:41,540 --> 00:23:42,300
(the police in Yunhe.)

442
00:23:43,380 --> 00:23:44,020
I bet

443
00:23:44,020 --> 00:23:45,180
they will be here soon.

444
00:23:45,500 --> 00:23:46,780
I told you to be more cautious.

445
00:23:47,260 --> 00:23:48,100
Why did you dig your own grave?

446
00:23:48,420 --> 00:23:49,700
Don't panic, Erliang.

447
00:23:50,340 --> 00:23:51,380
I have another way.

448
00:23:51,940 --> 00:23:52,500
Like I said,

449
00:23:52,500 --> 00:23:53,700
just get back here if you really can't manage it.

450
00:23:54,140 --> 00:23:54,540
No.

451
00:23:54,700 --> 00:23:55,580
Listen to me, Erliang.

452
00:23:57,580 --> 00:23:58,780
I know a gangster.

453
00:23:59,460 --> 00:24:00,540
He used to be a follower of K.

454
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:02,620
And he ever stole some goods from Dong.

455
00:24:03,580 --> 00:24:04,380
He's now

456
00:24:04,380 --> 00:24:05,500
in the rehab centre.

457
00:24:06,340 --> 00:24:07,300
I'm going to find him.

458
00:24:26,180 --> 00:24:30,580
[Police Station]

459
00:24:30,620 --> 00:24:31,500
Thank you.

460
00:24:31,700 --> 00:24:33,100
Seriously, thank you so much.

461
00:24:33,140 --> 00:24:34,540
I'll teach him a good lesson when we get home.

462
00:24:34,580 --> 00:24:35,580
It's okay since he's out now.

463
00:24:36,060 --> 00:24:36,980
Don't ever do drugs again.

464
00:24:39,020 --> 00:24:39,820
Chen Yu?

465
00:24:41,740 --> 00:24:42,100
Let's go.

466
00:24:42,460 --> 00:24:43,300
What? What's it?

467
00:24:43,540 --> 00:24:43,900
Hurry up.

468
00:24:44,300 --> 00:24:44,940
What's going on here?

469
00:24:45,140 --> 00:24:45,940
I need you to do me a favour.

470
00:24:46,180 --> 00:24:47,380
[Liu Guang, Yunhe Deshan West District
Police Station, Police Officer]

471
00:24:47,420 --> 00:24:47,980
Check on it.

472
00:24:48,460 --> 00:24:49,060
What?

473
00:24:49,060 --> 00:24:49,660
Check the surveillance footage.

474
00:24:50,300 --> 00:24:51,300
Which area?

475
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:53,180
The night of the 9th, Liugang Bridge intersection.

476
00:24:59,300 --> 00:25:02,060
[Friday, 2019-08-09]

477
00:25:24,620 --> 00:25:25,060
Well,

478
00:25:25,140 --> 00:25:26,460
are there any cameras from other angles?

479
00:25:27,620 --> 00:25:28,220
No.

480
00:25:28,500 --> 00:25:29,860
That's the only camera in this intersection.

481
00:25:30,860 --> 00:25:32,700
Can you enlarge this image

482
00:25:32,700 --> 00:25:33,540
and make it clearer?

483
00:25:36,060 --> 00:25:37,100
This is of highest-definition.

484
00:25:37,460 --> 00:25:38,620
After all, there's some distance

485
00:25:38,820 --> 00:25:39,340
between this location

486
00:25:39,340 --> 00:25:40,260
and the crime scene.

487
00:25:44,180 --> 00:25:44,940
Take a look at the next intersection.

488
00:25:47,900 --> 00:25:48,420
Fast forward.

489
00:26:05,140 --> 00:26:06,340
It's been twenty minutes.

490
00:26:06,340 --> 00:26:07,180
I don't think there's any clue.

491
00:26:13,580 --> 00:26:15,220
How far is this place from the crime scene?

492
00:26:16,540 --> 00:26:18,420
About two hundred meters.

493
00:26:20,100 --> 00:26:20,540
Guang.

494
00:26:21,420 --> 00:26:22,380
Here, give me a copy of it.

495
00:26:22,700 --> 00:26:23,100
Sure.

496
00:26:35,900 --> 00:26:36,860
(Let me out!)

497
00:26:37,940 --> 00:26:38,820
(Is anyone there?)

498
00:26:40,340 --> 00:26:41,300
Help!

499
00:26:43,300 --> 00:26:44,420
Let me out!

500
00:26:48,580 --> 00:26:49,500
Help!

501
00:26:53,660 --> 00:26:58,580
[Zhang, Drug Dealer]

502
00:26:58,700 --> 00:26:59,340
Xian.

503
00:26:59,740 --> 00:27:01,340
[Huang Wenlin aka Huang Daxian, Drug Dealer]

504
00:27:01,380 --> 00:27:02,420
I bet you didn't see this day coming

505
00:27:03,060 --> 00:27:04,380
when you gave me away.

506
00:27:04,620 --> 00:27:05,300
Who gave you away?

507
00:27:06,540 --> 00:27:07,940
I would never do that to you.

508
00:27:09,900 --> 00:27:10,740
Well,

509
00:27:10,860 --> 00:27:12,620
who asked from Changmao the pills?

510
00:27:16,420 --> 00:27:17,060
Spit it out!

511
00:27:18,700 --> 00:27:19,220
Who was it?

512
00:27:19,580 --> 00:27:20,340
I'll say it.

513
00:27:20,780 --> 00:27:21,860
It's Jianglei.

514
00:27:22,340 --> 00:27:23,260
He's a follower...

515
00:27:23,660 --> 00:27:24,540
A follower of Dong.

516
00:27:25,700 --> 00:27:27,020
He almost beat me to death on that day.

517
00:27:27,260 --> 00:27:28,260
I was left with no choice but to give you away.

518
00:27:35,740 --> 00:27:37,380
I know I was wrong, Xian.

519
00:27:37,980 --> 00:27:38,820
Please let me go.

520
00:27:40,460 --> 00:27:43,260
It's only natural for one to repay their debt.

521
00:27:43,700 --> 00:27:45,020
I could have waited for you.

522
00:27:45,460 --> 00:27:46,700
However, since you've given me away,

523
00:27:47,220 --> 00:27:48,500
you can't blame me for what I'm about to do.

524
00:27:49,380 --> 00:27:49,940
Xian.

525
00:27:50,100 --> 00:27:50,940
Don't light it, Xian!

526
00:27:51,020 --> 00:27:51,580
Xian!

527
00:27:51,900 --> 00:27:53,700
We're homies, Huang Daxian!

528
00:27:54,180 --> 00:27:55,300
Huang Daxian!

529
00:27:55,660 --> 00:27:56,620
Huang Daxian!

530
00:27:56,660 --> 00:27:57,780
Let me go!

531
00:27:58,060 --> 00:27:59,620
I'm going to kill you!

532
00:28:01,420 --> 00:28:02,380
[Yang Yi, Yunhe Public Security Bureau]

533
00:28:02,420 --> 00:28:03,500
[Counter Narcotics Unit, Police Officer]
Have you ever seen the man in this photo?

534
00:28:04,100 --> 00:28:04,860
I have.

535
00:28:05,260 --> 00:28:06,620
He was the one who got beaten up on that night.

536
00:28:07,220 --> 00:28:08,300
Was it the fight happened here

537
00:28:08,580 --> 00:28:09,420
on the night of the 9th August?

538
00:28:10,100 --> 00:28:10,940
Yes, the 9th of August.

539
00:28:11,220 --> 00:28:12,380
Do you remember

540
00:28:13,140 --> 00:28:13,780
the specific spot where the fight happened?

541
00:28:14,380 --> 00:28:15,020
Right at the middle here.

542
00:28:15,060 --> 00:28:16,180
[Yiming Skewers]

543
00:28:16,220 --> 00:28:17,460
Since it was a fight,
why didn't you make a police report?

544
00:28:18,020 --> 00:28:19,700
Well, it wasn't long

545
00:28:19,700 --> 00:28:20,780
before the both parties ran away.

546
00:28:20,900 --> 00:28:22,100
I then took a look at the surroundings.

547
00:28:22,380 --> 00:28:23,660
They didn't cause much damage.

548
00:28:23,980 --> 00:28:24,860
So I blamed it on my bad luck and let it slide.

549
00:28:25,060 --> 00:28:25,820
I'm running nothing but a small business here.

550
00:28:26,100 --> 00:28:27,220
Seriously, I wouldn't want to
get myself into trouble.

551
00:28:27,260 --> 00:28:28,180
Fine, I got it.

552
00:28:28,700 --> 00:28:29,060
Do make a police report at once

553
00:28:29,060 --> 00:28:29,460
Yang Yi.

554
00:28:29,460 --> 00:28:30,500
if there's anything.

555
00:28:30,940 --> 00:28:31,700
Look at how messy this car is.

556
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:32,820
I'm sure it's been days since it was on the road.

557
00:28:34,940 --> 00:28:35,900
It's been three days.

558
00:28:36,140 --> 00:28:37,140
What clues can we find?

559
00:28:37,620 --> 00:28:38,980
114, the car owner's number.

560
00:28:44,020 --> 00:28:45,140
It's written right there, no?

561
00:28:49,340 --> 00:28:49,820
Call the number.

562
00:28:51,940 --> 00:28:52,620
My sister said

563
00:28:52,820 --> 00:28:54,060
that you've been rather emotional lately.

564
00:28:54,540 --> 00:28:55,260
I think you've

565
00:28:55,260 --> 00:28:56,100
affected her to some extent.

566
00:28:57,780 --> 00:28:59,220
Well, I should have stayed out of your business.

567
00:29:00,780 --> 00:29:01,340
Yet what can I do?

568
00:29:01,340 --> 00:29:02,340
She's my sister after all.

569
00:29:03,100 --> 00:29:04,140
You can't do her wrong.

570
00:29:04,180 --> 00:29:04,740
Do you hear me?

571
00:29:07,140 --> 00:29:07,820
Hello?

572
00:29:11,780 --> 00:29:12,420
Who's that?

573
00:29:17,020 --> 00:29:17,580
Madam.

574
00:29:17,780 --> 00:29:18,820
[Jiang Lei, Drug Dealer]
I'm a friend of Gousheng.

575
00:29:18,940 --> 00:29:19,780
Is he home?

576
00:29:20,140 --> 00:29:20,940
Are you looking for him?

577
00:29:28,220 --> 00:29:29,900
Go ahead, run. You can't escape.

578
00:29:30,060 --> 00:29:30,500
Lei.

579
00:29:30,540 --> 00:29:31,540
[Gou Sheng, Drug Dealer]

580
00:29:31,780 --> 00:29:33,180
I was wrong, Lei!

581
00:29:35,420 --> 00:29:36,020
Lei!

582
00:29:37,700 --> 00:29:38,260
